9.text: Pasindu is a student of Kajulanda M.V. He has always done well in his studies and various extra-curricular activities of the school-especially in sports. Recently, he got through the GCE (A/L) examination with three A passes. So, the school organized a felicitation ceremony for him. The following is the interview that Charith, a member of the school media unit, had with Pasindu just after the ceremony.

10.text: Charith: Good morning, Pasindu! Today is a special day for you. Tell me, What are your thoughts at the moment?

11.text: Pasindu: I feel really happy and honoured. In fact, this is one of the happiest days of my life.

12.text: Charith: You’re a role model to all of us. You have been a senior prefect, the captain of the school volleyball team and a school cadet. With all that, you managed to get through your A/L s with flying colours. How did you do all this?
